# ADaM Programming

## Overview

This folder contains SAS programs used to derive analysis-ready datasets from the finalized SDTM domains for the HTN001 study.

## Planned Analysis Datasets

| Dataset | Description                             | Status      |
| ------- | --------------------------------------- | ----------- |
| ADSL    | Subject-Level Analysis Dataset          | In Progress |
| ADVS    | Vital Signs Analysis Dataset            | Planned     |
| ADLB    | Laboratory Analysis Dataset             | Planned     |
| ADAE    | Adverse Event Analysis Dataset          | Planned     |
| ADCM    | Concomitant Medication Analysis Dataset | Planned     |

## Key Derivations

* Treatment variables
* Population flags
* Baseline variables
* Change from baseline
* Percent change
* Analysis dates
* Analysis visits

These datasets will be used directly for TLF generation.
